---
const calcData = [
  { label: "Direct answer in first 60 words", desc: "Lead with a self-contained 40–80 word answer block", pts: 15 },
  { label: "H2 headings phrased as questions", desc: "At least 3 of your main headers should be searchable questions", pts: 10 },
  { label: "FAQ section with 4+ questions", desc: "Each answer 2–3 sentences, specific, citation-ready", pts: 10 },
  { label: "Comparison table included", desc: "At least one structured table with 3+ rows and 3+ columns", pts: 11 },
  { label: "1 table or bullet list per ~150 words", desc: "Consistent structured content throughout the post body", pts: 10 },
  { label: "Author bio with credentials + link", desc: "Verifiable role, past companies, LinkedIn or credential URL", pts: 10 },
  { label: "External expert citation included", desc: "Named expert or report cited with attribution", pts: 10 },
  { label: "Statistic with source + year", desc: "Specific number with source name and year", pts: 8 },
  { label: '"Last Updated" date visible', desc: "Shown at top of post, month + year minimum", pts: 7 },
  { label: "Internal links to topic cluster", desc: "Links to at least one pillar page and one related post", pts: 9 },
];
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>GEO Optimization Checklist & Template | Devi's Lab</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #F5F2EC;
    --surface: #FDFCF9;
    --ink: #1A1814;
    --ink-muted: #5C5648;
    --accent: #D45C2E;
    --accent-light: #F2E8E2;
    --accent2: #2E6B5C;
    --accent2-light: #E2F0EC;
    --rule: #DDD8CE;
    --score-low: #C94F3A;
    --score-mid: #D4882E;
    --score-high: #2E6B5C;
    --mono: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    --sans: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    --serif: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .site-header {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    padding: 14px 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .site-header .logo { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--accent); }
  .site-header .badge {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    padding: 60px 40px 50px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: 'GEO';
    position: absolute;
    right: -20px;
    top: -30px;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 200px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    pointer-events: none;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 52px);
    line-height: 1.15;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .hero-desc {
    color: rgba(245,242,236,0.65);
    max-width: 520px;
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .hero-meta-item {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(245,242,236,0.5);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .hero-meta-item span { color: var(--bg); font-weight: 500; }

  /* LAYOUT */
  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  /* TABS */
  .tabs-nav {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 0 40px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 50;
  }
  .tab-btn {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 16px 24px 14px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .tab-btn:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  .tab-btn.active {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .tab-content { display: none; padding: 48px 40px; }
  .tab-content.active { display: block; }

  /* SECTION HEADERS */
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 28px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .section-desc {
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    max-width: 540px;
  }

  /* TECHNIQUE CARDS */
  .techniques-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) { .techniques-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .technique-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 22px 24px;
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .technique-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--accent);
  }
  .technique-card .num {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    display: block;
  }
  .technique-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 17px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .technique-card p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .technique-card .impact {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .impact.high { background: var(--accent2-light); color: var(--accent2); }
  .impact.med { background: #FFF3E0; color: #B06000; }
  .technique-card .example-box {
    margin-top: 14px;
    background: var(--bg);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .technique-card .example-box strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* BEFORE / AFTER */
  .ba-container { margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .ba-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) { .ba-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .ba-panel {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: var(--surface);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ba-panel-header {
    padding: 12px 20px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .ba-panel.before .ba-panel-header { background: #FEF2F2; color: #9B3A3A; }
  .ba-panel.after .ba-panel-header { background: var(--accent2-light); color: var(--accent2); }
  .ba-panel-body { padding: 20px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .ba-panel-body code {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 1px 5px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .ba-panel-body .field-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin-top: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    display: block;
  }
  .ba-panel-body .field-value {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .ba-panel.after .field-value { color: var(--ink); }

  .geo-score-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .score-low { background: #FEF2F2; color: var(--score-low); }
  .score-high { background: var(--accent2-light); color: var(--accent2); }
  .score-circle {
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .score-low .score-circle { background: var(--score-low); }
  .score-high .score-circle { background: var(--score-high); }

  /* CITATION EXAMPLE */
  .citation-box {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    padding: 24px 28px;
    margin: 24px 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  .citation-box::before {
    content: 'PERPLEXITY CITATION SIMULATION';
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--accent);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .citation-box .cited-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(245,242,236,0.85);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .citation-box .cite-source {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(245,242,236,0.4);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    padding-top: 12px;
  }
  .citation-box .cite-source span { color: var(--accent); }

  /* SCORE CALCULATOR */
  .calculator {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 32px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .calc-items { margin: 24px 0; }
  .calc-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .calc-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .calc-checkbox {
    width: 20px; height: 20px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 2px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    background: white;
  }
  .calc-checkbox.checked {
    background: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }
  .calc-checkbox.checked::after {
    content: '✓';
    color: white;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .calc-item-text { flex: 1; }
  .calc-item-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .calc-item-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-muted); }
  .calc-item-pts {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }
  .calc-item-pts.earned { color: var(--accent2); font-weight: 500; }

  .score-display {
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .score-number {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 64px;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }
  .score-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .score-bar-track {
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--rule);
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .score-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 3px;
    transition: width 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), background 0.3s;
    width: 0%;
  }
  .score-verdict {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .score-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
    background: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .btn:hover { background: var(--ink); color: var(--bg); }
  .btn.primary { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); color: white; }
  .btn.primary:hover { background: #B84E24; border-color: #B84E24; }

  /* TEMPLATE SECTION */
  .template-block {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .template-block-header {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    padding: 12px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  .template-block-header .req {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .template-block-body { padding: 20px 24px; }
  .template-field {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px dashed var(--rule);
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    cursor: text;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .template-field:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--ink); }
  .template-field .placeholder { color: #B5AFA7; font-style: italic; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: rgba(245,242,236,0.5);
    padding: 32px 40px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: gap;
  }
  footer a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); margin: 40px 0; }

  /* PRINT */
  @media print {
    .tabs-nav, .site-header { display: none; }
    .tab-content { display: block !important; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="site-header">
  <span class="logo">Devi's Lab</span>
  <span style="opacity:0.4">devislabai.com</span>
  <span class="badge">Free Resource</span>
</header>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">Resource Template · GEO Series</div>
  <h1>The GEO Optimization<br><em>Checklist & Template</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-desc">10 techniques to make your blog citable by ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Google SGE. Includes a before/after LinkedIn example and interactive GEO score calculator (out of 100).</p>
  <div class="hero-meta">
    <div class="hero-meta-item">By <span>Devi Priya K</span></div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">Updated <span>May 2026</span></div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">Format <span>Interactive Checklist</span></div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">Time to complete <span>~20 min per post</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<nav class="tabs-nav">
  <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('techniques', this)">10 Techniques</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('beforeafter', this)">Before / After</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('calculator', this)">GEO Score</button>
</nav>

<!-- TAB 1: TECHNIQUES -->
<div id="tab-techniques" class="tab-content active">
  <div class="section-label">The ACS Framework · 10 Techniques</div>
  <div class="section-title">Make Any Post AI-Citable</div>
  <p class="section-desc">Each technique maps to one of three pillars: Answerability, Clarity, or Signal. Apply all 10 for maximum citation potential.</p>

  <div class="techniques-grid">

    <div class="technique-card">
      <span class="num">01 · ANSWERABILITY</span>
      <h3>Direct Answer Block</h3>
      <p>Lead with a 40–80 word summary that directly answers the post's core question. AI engines scan for this first.</p>
      <span class="impact high">High Impact</span>
      <div class="example-box">
        <strong>Format</strong>
        <strong>Quick Answer:</strong> [Topic] is [definition]. The best approach is [X] because [Y]. Start with [Z].
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="technique-card">
      <span class="num">02 · ANSWERABILITY</span>
      <h3>Question-Phrased H2 Headers</h3>
      <p>Rewrite all H2s as questions that match how people actually search. AI engines match queries to question headers directly.</p>
      <span class="impact high">High Impact</span>
      <div class="example-box">
        <strong>Before → After</strong>
        "CRM Options" → "What Is the Best CRM for Startups in 2026?"
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="technique-card">
      <span class="num">03 · ANSWERABILITY</span>
      <h3>FAQ Section</h3>
      <p>Add 4–6 questions your reader would actually ask. Each answer should be 2–3 sentences, self-contained, and citation-ready.</p>
      <span class="impact high">High Impact</span>
      <div class="example-box">
        <strong>Structure</strong>
        Q: [Specific question]
        A: [Direct 2–3 sentence answer with a specific detail or number]
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="technique-card">
      <span class="num">04 · CLARITY</span>
      <h3>Comparison Tables</h3>
      <p>One structured table per major comparison. Tables are the most-cited format in AI answers — they give engines clean, structured data to surface.</p>
      <span class="impact high">High Impact</span>
      <div class="example-box">
        <strong>Minimum columns</strong>
        Tool | Price | Best For | Key Limitation
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="technique-card">
      <span class="num">05 · CLARITY</span>
      <h3>Bullet-Point Summaries</h3>
      <p>After every major section, add a 3–5 point summary. Keep each bullet under 20 words. These get lifted directly into AI responses.</p>
      <span class="impact med">Med Impact</span>
      <div class="example-box">
        <strong>Use for</strong>
        Key takeaways, step lists, feature comparisons, pros/cons
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="technique-card">
      <span class="num">06 · CLARITY</span>
      <h3>Named Mini-Frameworks</h3>
      <p>Give your core idea a name. "The ACS Framework" is more citable than "my approach." Named frameworks get attributed and repeated.</p>
      <span class="impact high">High Impact</span>
      <div class="example-box">
        <strong>Pattern</strong>
        [Acronym] = [3 pillars]. E.g., ACS = Answerability, Clarity, Signal.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="technique-card">
      <span class="num">07 · SIGNAL</span>
      <h3>Authoritative Quotes & Citations</h3>
      <p>Cite 1–2 external experts by name and link. AI engines use external citations as a trust signal — it shows your post is part of a larger conversation.</p>
      <span class="impact med">Med Impact</span>
      <div class="example-box">
        <strong>Format</strong>
        Per [Expert Name] ([Source]): "[paraphrased claim with attribution]."
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="technique-card">
      <span class="num">08 · SIGNAL</span>
      <h3>Statistics With Sources</h3>
      <p>Include 2–3 specific statistics with clear attribution. Numbers get cited far more than vague claims. "73% of startups" beats "many startups."</p>
      <span class="impact med">Med Impact</span>
      <div class="example-box">
        <strong>Format</strong>
        [Stat] — [Source], [Year]. E.g., "73% of SMBs use CRM — Salesforce State of Sales, 2025."
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="technique-card">
      <span class="num">09 · SIGNAL</span>
      <h3>Author Bio + Credentials</h3>
      <p>Every post needs a byline with verifiable credentials. AI engines use author authority to decide whether to cite content. Link to LinkedIn or published work.</p>
      <span class="impact high">High Impact</span>
      <div class="example-box">
        <strong>Format</strong>
        By [Name], [Role] (ex-[Company]). [Credential 1], [Credential 2]. [LinkedIn link]
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="technique-card">
      <span class="num">10 · SIGNAL</span>
      <h3>Topic Cluster + Internal Links</h3>
      <p>Link every post to a pillar page and at least one related satellite post. Topic clusters signal topical authority to both search engines and AI crawlers.</p>
      <span class="impact med">Med Impact</span>
      <div class="example-box">
        <strong>Structure</strong>
        Pillar: "What Is GEO?" → Satellite: "GEO Checklist" → Satellite: "ACS Framework"
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div style="background:var(--accent-light); border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); padding: 20px 24px; font-size:13px; color: var(--ink-muted);">
    <strong style="display:block; font-family:var(--mono); font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:8px;">Quick Start Rule</strong>
    Apply techniques 01, 02, 03, and 04 first. These four have the highest citation impact and take under 30 minutes per post. Add 05–10 in a second pass.
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TAB 2: BEFORE / AFTER -->
